{
  "stem": "22174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when she left her home toward the south of Germany, her family said to her, don't-- just don't bring out a Prussian.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's exactly what she brought.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] How did the traveling salesman get your mother's picture?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was her brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my mother was a half-orphan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her father had died years before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know when.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they went looking for a husband, probably for her, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And otherwise our family life-- my parents had a store [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] which my father took over from my grandfather, who had started working in a very small, little store in a one-story building with a tipped roof.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they lived in the back of the store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a very small store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when my grandfather died, my father came back from Berlin and to take over the store.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the landlord of that house made an agreement with my father that he would put up a new three-story, modern building on the condition that my father would enlarge the store.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's what he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the store became quite a sizable store, relatively, to the small town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A very well-known store.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father and my mother worked together in the store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had a maid that cooked and cleaned and lived in the same house, upstairs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] then I remember being sent to kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother had to push me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I cried first time, first day when she left me alone there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And then I went to public school.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
